---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume | Diego Porras Vera" description="Recruiter-friendly resume: web dev, automation, multimedia production. EN/ES.">
  <header class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
    <div>
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-400">Resume</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Diego Porras Vera</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-zinc-300">Brookline, MA · Work Authorization (U.S.) · English / Spanish</p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex gap-2">
      <a class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 px-4 py-2 text-sm hover:bg-zinc-900" href="/contact">Contact</a>
      <a class="rounded-xl bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-zinc-950 hover:bg-zinc-200" href="/portfolio">Portfolio</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="mt-10 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-5">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-6">
        <h2 class="font-semibold">Professional summary</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-300">
          Systems Engineer with practical experience in modern web development, automation, and multimedia production.
          Strong focus on scalable architecture (client/server), REST APIs, JWT authentication, role-based access, and
          admin dashboards. Comfortable collaborating across technical and operational teams (EN/ES).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-6">
        <h2 class="font-semibold">Experience</h2>

        <div class="mt-4 space-y-6 text-sm text-zinc-300">
          <div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2">
              <span class="font-medium text-zinc-100">CYBER BYTE (Perú) — Digital Architecture & Development</span>
              <span class="text-zinc-400">Project / Ongoing</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
              <li>Built web + backend architecture with REST APIs, JWT auth, roles/permissions, and admin dashboards.</li>
              <li>Designed inventory automation approach and shared data model for web/app usage.</li>
              <li>Deployed cloud infrastructure (Railway) and structured system for scalability.</li>
              <li>Cross-border collaboration: Diego (U.S.) dev/tech, Franco (Perú) sales, Pamela (Perú) admin/inventory.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2">
              <span class="font-medium text-zinc-100">DJ GOX / SONICA Entertainment — Digital Operations</span>
              <span class="text-zinc-400">Ongoing</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
              <li>Brand and website development; marketing automation for promotions and booking workflows.</li>
              <li>Created digital assets (flyers, ads, social content) and production pipelines for event marketing.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2">
              <span class="font-medium text-zinc-100">Dunkin’ Donuts (MA) — Operations & Customer Service</span>
              <span class="text-zinc-400">Current</span>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-2 text-zinc-300">
              Support role while building long-term technology and creative projects.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-6">
        <h2 class="font-semibold">Education</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-zinc-300">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2">
            <span class="font-medium text-zinc-100">Universidad Continental (Perú)</span>
            <span class="text-zinc-400">Completed</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-1">B.S. in Systems Engineering & Informatics</p>

          <div class="mt-4">
            <p class="text-zinc-400">Key academic areas</p>
            <div class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              {[
                "Software development",
                "Information systems",
                "Databases",
                "Software architecture",
                "Networks & security fundamentals",
                "Tech project management",
              ].map((s) => (
                <span class="rounded-full border border-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-zinc-300">{s}</span>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="space-y-5">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-6">
        <h2 class="font-semibold">Tech stack</h2>

        <div class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-300">
          <div>
            <p class="text-zinc-400">Frontend</p>
            <div class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              {["HTML5", "CSS3", "Tailwind CSS", "JavaScript (ES6+)", "React", "Next.js", "Astro", "Vite"].map((t) => (
                <span class="rounded-full border border-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-zinc-300">{t}</span>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="text-zinc-400">Backend</p>
            <div class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              {["Node.js", "Express.js", "REST APIs", "JWT Auth", "Roles/Permissions"].map((t) => (
                <span class="rounded-full border border-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-zinc-300">{t}</span>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="text-zinc-400">Databases</p>
            <div class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              {["MongoDB", "Data modeling", "Frontend–backend integration"].map((t) => (
                <span class="rounded-full border border-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-zinc-300">{t}</span>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-6">
        <h2 class="font-semibold">Automation</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-300">
          Advanced use of n8n for marketing automation, platform integrations, message flows, and conditional logic to reduce cost and increase efficiency.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-6">
        <h2 class="font-semibold">Multimedia</h2>
        <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs text-zinc-300">
          {["DaVinci Resolve Studio 20", "Adobe Creative Cloud", "Final Cut Pro", "Affinity Suite", "Motion graphics", "Tracking/VFX"].map((t) => (
            <span class="rounded-full border border-zinc-800 px-3 py-1">{t}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-6">
        <h2 class="font-semibold">3D / XR</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-zinc-300">
          3D modeling (Blender). Interest and practice in Unity and XR/VR experiences—combining engineering with visual creativity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
